&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;At Prodigal, we are driven by a singular, unrelenting purpose: to transform how consumer finance companies engage with their customers and, in turn, drive successful outcomes for all.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About The Team:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
