&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Overview:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Strategy &amp;amp; Operations Lead, you will own end-to-end consumer engagement and collections strategy for a portfolio of 3-4 clients. This is a hands-on role where you’ll move from problem identification to strategy design to execution, directly operating workflows across various engagement channels. You will work directly with senior client leaders, including CXOs, owning both strategic outcomes and the relationship.&amp;nbsp;In a span of 6-12 months from joining, you&#39;ll have the opportunity to hire and lead analysts to amplify your experience and drive more impact.&lt;/p&gt;
